ZH: 这个古老的习俗一直在我们家族中传承下来。
EN: This ancient tradition has been passed down in our family for generations.

ZH: 各种技艺都需要被传承，否则会失传。
EN: Various skills need to be inherited, otherwise they will be lost.

ZH: 传承文化遗产是我们每个人的责任。
EN: Inheriting cultural heritage is the responsibility of each of us.

ZH: 这家企业在行业中有着悠久的传承历史。
EN: This company has a long tradition in the industry.

ZH: 希望我们能传承下来这一份友谊。
EN: I hope we can pass down this friendship.

ZH: 传承优秀传统是我们这个行业的目标之一。
EN: Inheriting excellent traditions is one of the goals of our industry.

ZH: 我们应该努力传承先辈们的智慧和勇气。
EN: We should strive to inherit the wisdom and courage of our ancestors.

ZH: 这个项目的目标是传承悠久的历史和文化。
EN: The goal of this project is to carry on the long history and culture.

ZH: 责任传承需要由每个人来承担。
EN: Responsibility for inheritance needs to be carried by everyone.

ZH: 这本书传承了作者对生活的思考。
EN: This book inherits the author's thoughts on life.

ZH: 我们要将这份爱传承给下一代。
EN: We want to pass down this love to the next generation.

ZH: 传承无形的精神财富比传承物质更加重要。
EN: Inheriting intangible spiritual wealth is more important than inheriting material wealth.

ZH: 这首歌传承了民族的音乐传统。
EN: This song inherits the musical traditions of the nation.

ZH: 这个节日有着深厚的文化传承。
EN: This festival has a profound cultural heritage.

ZH: 我们应该尊重并传承每一个民族的文化。
EN: We should respect and pass down the cultures of every nation.

ZH: 这个家族传承了纯朴的农业生活。
EN: This family has inherited a simple agricultural life.

ZH: 文学作品是文化传承的一种方式。
EN: Literary works are a way of cultural inheritance.

ZH: 我们要传承优秀的学术传统。
EN: We want to inherit excellent academic traditions.

ZH: 这家公司一直坚持着技术传承。
EN: This company has always insisted on passing down technology.

ZH: 传承着家族财富和荣誉是每个子孙的使命。
EN: Inheriting family wealth and honor is the mission of every descendant.
